if its not part of the trial i would not consider it said 
the man 
one man said that he would regard a decision by barry not to run 
for reelection as an admission of guilt he said he thinks barry 
should resign because the publicity surrounding the investigation 
and prosecution of the mayor has hurt the city that man was 
one of seven excluded from the jury pool 
