dcalif joseph kennedy dmass john lafalce dny jim 
lightfoot riowa romano mazzoli dky bill nelson dfla 
charles rangel dny dan rostenkowski dill and denny smith 
rore not voting by tradition was house speaker thomas s foley 
dwash 
