the only way to conclude a deal in a situation where there is 
such a pluralism in europe of types of weapons 
but konarski and plaisant said there were still many issues to 
be resolved before a final agreement can be signed konarski said 
the issue of ceilings and definitions on aircraft and helicopters 
and terms for verification still must be resolved 
