used against the opposition 
june 13 police break up the anticommunist demonstration at 
university square beating some protesters rioting erupts and 
police open fire at least four people are killed 
june 14 more clashes reported tens of thousands of workers 
turn out in support of the government some beating members of the 
opposition and ransacking opposition parties offices 
