controversial aspects of the economic program presented to the 
supreme soviet by premier nikolai ryzhkov last month 
on wednesday the supreme soviet gave gorbachev a mandate to 
speed economic reforms it said the government had until october to 
prepare more radical measures to move the country toward a market 
economy 
